{"tid":873220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聽朝可否不要跌 另創新高","createTime":"2018-10-23T09:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T06:39:14.000Z","uid":93821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3daaa92c5acd98a66c09ef437f8ddc8a79ae6117","tid":873220,"uid":93821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝可否不要跌 另創新高<br />\n升矢可否不要無 令我乞討<br />\n恆指 即使早知 升市那味道<br />\n卻想完美到 去違抗負數</span><br />\n<br />\n那段年月也得倒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資金以後也安好<br />\n最好 我入貨的</span> 任何面容都 不會跌<br />\n<br />\n為何 在熊二裡 在遊上去 突然又插去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盲好 一個事情 可以兌現時 你又再安睡<br />\n祈求 慢熊別去 慢牛萬歲 別隨便割去<br />\n恆指 這個壞人 偏卻決絕如許<br />\n離場慢些 也不許</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好問我邊間教會"},{"pid":"f1acc3af7d547019ffe20db45c41504c19ebe162","tid":873220,"uid":99473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？"},{"pid":"cafebf272b1003b6a323ea9088e7c89e8ba88e81","tid":873220,"uid":93821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1</blockquote>"}]}